{"tid":1326102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時眾籌提告香港警務署以及部分警員在新城市違法圍捕市民","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:57:31.000Z","uid":160638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"accb484dccec6c2fa0fd8d4b1af77f3d1c8f19e7","tid":1326102,"uid":160638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"在7月14日沙田新城市廣場警員違法圍捕市民一事,目前我們可以依賴司法覆核去控告香港警務署,但司法覆核通常用於推翻政府部分決定,覆核成功不帶任何罰則(有錯請指證),但不知覆核結果能否幫助因714事件而被補的抗爭者脱罪,希望大家俾意見分析下係咪應該做民事訴訟先,還是一齊做向警隊施壓。<br />\n民事訴訟(<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/civilCase/civil_case/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FcivilCase%2Fcivil_case%2F&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=ed8fa75a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/civilCase/civil_case/</a>)可以入民事法嘅罪行,刑事訴訟只能由律政師提告,一般市民大眾要投訴警察並告刑事罪行需要向投訴警察課投訴,並由監警會審核(有錯請指證),詳情如下<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/142498/%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E6%A1%88-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E9%84%AD%E4%BB%B2%E6%81%86-%E8%8B%A5%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E8%AA%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B-%E6%AF%94%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F%E6%9B%B4%E5%85%B7%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F142498%2F%25E6%259C%25B1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%2584%25AD%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E6%2581%2586-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%25A8%259F%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%2585%25B7%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=469f0d37\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/142498/%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E6%A1%88-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E9%84%AD%E4%BB%B2%E6%81%86-%E8%8B%A5%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E8%AA%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B-%E6%AF%94%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F%E6%9B%B4%E5%85%B7%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/132273/%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E6%A1%88-01%E5%80%A1%E8%AD%B0-%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%BF%AB%E6%AC%8A-%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E6%9C%89%E7%89%99%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%2F132273%2F%25E6%259C%25B1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E6%25A1%2588-01%25E5%2580%25A1%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2599%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%2599%258E&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=a56c09d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/132273/%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E6%A1%88-01%E5%80%A1%E8%AD%B0-%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%BF%AB%E6%AC%8A-%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E6%9C%89%E7%89%99%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E</a>。<br />\n<br />\n示威者可否在透過司法覆核或民事訴訟裁定法律權利被侵犯後,謀定刑事訴訟?<br />\n<br />\n我認為那怕失敗也要做下去,訴訟可以向警員施加心理壓力,令他們不敢肆意妄為,<br />\n請大家俾d建議同意見"},{"pid":"53876b6a0250cc97dac440d8fe14f1784680bc52","tid":1326102,"uid":160638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"我認為警員無出示委任證,假若有人因這些警員而受傷,所申索的賠償隨時由該名警員自行承擔"}]}